DOC.criteria: Asymptomatic subject ( without somatosensory peripheral pain ) recruit study . Subjects must sign informed consent . Subjects heart failure nervous system disease exclude study . Additional exclusion include osteoporosis , diabetes , pregnancy , vascular insufficiency , history joint replacement therapy . Subjects medical treatment , surgery trauma within six month exclude .
